770
00:52:19,330 --> 00:52:21,310
- There's, uh, there's someone down there. - We've got you--
- 下...下面有人 - 你安全了...

771
00:52:21,320 --> 00:52:22,560
- What? - Fuck.
- 什么？- 操

772
